    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, preserved in a state that defies its tenure. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paintwork, reflects a commitment to absolute excellence. Mechanical integrity is beyond reproach, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is an acquisition for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
